                                  "' has unexpected 'exclude' sub-param(s): '"
                                  + selectorConfig.getName(0) + "'");
        }
        selectorConfig.remove("exclude");
      }
      if (0 < selectorConfig.size()) {
        throw new SolrException(SERVER_ERROR, "Init param '" + SOURCE_PARAM +
